'''氯乙腈'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为ClCH<sub>2</sub>CN，它是无色液体，是乙腈的一个氢原子被氯取代的产物。实际上，它是通过氯乙酰胺脱水制得的。<ref>{{cite journal |first1=D. B.|last1=Reisner|first2=E. C. |last2=Horning|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.030.0022|title=Chloroacetonitrile|journal=Organic Syntheses|year=1950|volume=30|page=22}}</ref>它是烷基化试剂，应当小心使用。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.15227/orgsyn.086.0001|title=Preparation of (3,5-Dimethoxy-1-Phenyl-Cyclohexa-2,5-Dienyl)-Acetonitrile Through Birch Reductive Alkylation (BRA)|journal=Organic Syntheses|year=2009|volume=86|page=1|first1=Raphaël|last1=Lebeuf|first2=Muriel |last2=Berlande|first3=Frédéric|last3=Robert|first4=Yannick|last4=Landais
}}</ref>

氯乙腈也可由[[乙腈|乙腈]]和[[二氯化二硫|二氯化二硫]]反应得到。它进一步氯化可以得到[[二氯乙腈|二氯乙腈]]，并可和二氯化二硫发生环加成反应，得到{{le|4,5-二氯-1,2,3-二噻唑鎓氯化物|4,5-Dichloro-1,2,3-dithiazolium chloride}}：<ref name=Rees>{{cite journal |doi=10.1002/jhet.5570290306|title=Polysulfur-Nitrogen Heterocyclic Chemistry|year=1992|last1=Rees|first1=Charles W.|journal=Journal of Heterocyclic Chemistry|volume=29|issue=3|pages=639–651}}</ref>
:Cl<sub>2</sub>CHCN  +  S<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>  →  [S<sub>2</sub>NC<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>]Cl  +  HCl

它和[[苯胺|苯胺]]在[[碳酸钾|碳酸钾]]、[[碘化钠|碘化钠]]的存在下于乙腈中反应，可以得到N-氰甲基苯胺<!-- 别名：苯氨基乙腈 -->。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry - A European Journal|volume=24|issue=34|language=en|date=2018-06-18|pages=8535–8541|doi=10.1002/chem.201801163|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/chem.201801163|title=Design and Synthesis of Iminosydnones for Fast Click and Release Reactions with Cycloalkynes|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=Margaux Riomet, Elodie Decuypere, Karine Porte, Sabrina Bernard, Lucie Plougastel, Sergii Kolodych, Davide Audisio, Frédéric Taran}}</ref>它和[[三苯基膦|三苯基膦]]在[[甲苯|甲苯]]中回流，可以得到三苯基氰甲基氯化𬭸。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Heterocyclic Chemistry|volume=52|issue=3|language=en|date=2015-05|pages=764–772|doi=10.1002/jhet.2186|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/jhet.2186|title=Synthesis and Antimicrobial Activity of N -Aryl-4-(cyano/alkoxycarbonyl)-5-(pyridin-3-yl)-1 H /3 H -1,2,3-triazole Derivatives: Synthesis of N-Aryl-5-(pyridin-3-yl)-4-(cyano/alkoxycarbonyl)-1,2,3-triazoles|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=Jayaram Reddy Komsani, Sreenivas Avula, Satish Koppireddi, Pranay Kumar Koochana, Murty Usn, Rambabu Yadla}}</ref>

